<li>
<i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>옴, 닭살, 소름</dt><br>
<dd>reflex erection of hairs of the skin in response to cold or emotional stress or skin irritation</dd><br>
<dd><i>synonyms</i>: pilomotor reflex, gooseflesh, goose bump, goosebump, goose pimple, goose skin, horripilation, goose flesh, goose pimples, goose bumps</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>
